    "whoUses": "Endocrinologists, primary care physicians, and internal medicine doctors use this code when managing type 1 diabetes patients with elevated blood sugar levels. It commonly appears on EOB statements for patients with type 1 diabetes seeking routine care, insulin adjustments, or evaluation of uncontrolled blood sugar.",
