    "plainEnglish": "This code indicates that your body has problems affecting multiple endocrine glands—the hormone-producing organs like the thyroid, adrenal glands, and pancreas—but the specific combination or underlying cause hasn't been clearly identified or documented. When several of these glands aren't working properly at the same time, it can cause a range of symptoms depending on which hormones are affected, such as fatigue, weight changes, or blood sugar problems. Your doctor likely needs more testing or specialist evaluation to pinpoint exactly which glands are involved and what's causing the problem.",
