    "shortDesc": "Other obesity due to excess calories",
    "longDesc": "Other obesity due to excess calories",
    "plainEnglish": "This code indicates that you are overweight due to consuming more calories than your body burns off—essentially an energy imbalance where food intake exceeds energy expenditure. This is the most common form of obesity and can result from dietary habits, sedentary lifestyle, or a combination of both, and it's distinct from obesity caused by specific medical conditions like hormonal disorders or genetic syndromes. You might experience weight gain, difficulty with physical activity, and related health concerns like joint stress or sleep problems.",
