    "whoUses": "Gastroenterologists, hospitalists, nutritionists, and intensive care specialists use this code when documenting overfeeding or excessive nutritional support in hospitalized or long-term care patients. It appears less commonly on patient EOB statements but may show up in hospital bills or when patients have insurance questions about their nutritional support therapy.",
