    "plainEnglish": "Your body normally breaks down fats from food into fatty acids, which it uses for energy and other vital functions. This code indicates a metabolic disorder affecting how your body processes or uses these fatty acids, but the specific type of disorder hasn't been identified yet. You might experience fatigue, muscle weakness, liver problems, or neurological symptoms depending on which fatty acids aren't being processed correctly.",
