    "whoUses": "Neurologists, genetic specialists, and endocrinologists diagnose and manage adrenomyeloneuropathy. This code appears less frequently on patient EOBs since it's a rare genetic condition, but it's used in hospital charts, specialty clinic notes, and when billing for genetic testing or specialized neurological evaluations related to this diagnosis.",
