    "plainEnglish": "Your body normally breaks down proteins into amino acids and uses them for many vital functions. This code means you have some kind of problem with how your body processes amino acids, but the specific type hasn't been identified yet. You might experience symptoms like developmental delays, intellectual disability, muscle weakness, or other metabolic problems depending on which amino acids are affected.",
