    "whoUses": "Pediatric neurologists, geneticists, and metabolic disease specialists typically diagnose and manage GM2 gangliosidosis; this code rarely appears on patient EOBs since it represents a rare genetic condition usually identified in childhood through specialized genetic testing and enzyme analysis rather than routine billing.",
