    "whoUses": "Pediatricians, neurologists, geneticists, and metabolic disease specialists use this code when diagnosing and managing affected children. It rarely appears on routine patient EOBs but is commonly seen in specialist referrals, genetic testing claims, and during treatment consultations at centers specializing in lysosomal storage disorders.",
