    "plainEnglish": "Your body breaks down proteins and other compounds into smaller pieces called purines and pyrimidines, which are used to make DNA and RNA. When this breakdown process doesn't work correctly, harmful substances can build up in your blood and tissues, potentially causing problems like gout, kidney stones, or other complications. This code means you have a problem with how your body processes these compounds, but the specific type hasn't been clearly identified yet.",
