    "whoUses": "Nephrologists (kidney specialists), endocrinologists, and primary care doctors commonly use this code when managing patients with chronic kidney disease, diabetes, or other metabolic disorders that affect blood acid levels. This code frequently appears on EOB statements for patients with chronic conditions requiring ongoing monitoring and treatment adjustments.",
